OL,3,C'Everything is worse': MS stem cell
OL,4,Ctreatment leaves man with side effects
OL,6,FMartin describes the treatment as
OL,7,Fbeing the hardest thing he has ever
OL,8,Fdone, but all seemed to be going well
OL,9,Funtil he left hospital.
OL,11,FHe then suddenly lost the ability to
OL,12,Fwalk and was diagnosed with a viral
OL,13,Finfection. He was rushed back into
OL,14,Fhospital, where treatment got the
OL,15,Fvirus under control, but it's had a
OL,16,Fhuge impact on his health.
OL,18,FMartin says: "Everything is worse.
OL,19,FWalking is so much harder. Ears, eyes,
OL,20,Fmotor skills, cognitive ability, that
OL,21,Fhas all suddenly tumbled down."
