OL,3,C'Everything is worse': MS stem cell
OL,4,Ctreatment leaves man with side effects
OL,6,F"I just struggle to do everyday things
OL,7,Flike getting around the house. I've
OL,8,Falso lost a lot of dexterity in my
OL,9,Fhand. I'm concerned I won't be able to
OL,10,Fwork."
OL,12,FThe treatment is known to have a lot
OL,13,Fof side effects but the severity of
OL,14,Fthe decline was not something Martin
OL,15,Fexpected and he's struggling to cope
OL,16,Fwith his new reality.
OL,18,FThe only hope is that although his
OL,19,Fsymptoms are worse, the treatment may
OL,20,Fstill halt the progression of the MS,
OL,21,Fbut that is very uncertain.
