OL,3,C'Everything is worse': MS stem cell
OL,4,Ctreatment leaves man with side effects
OL,6,FNobody can give him any guarantees
OL,7,Fabout his future, all he can do is
OL,8,Fhope things improve.
OL,10,FMartin says: "It's a difficult thing
OL,11,Fto process. Though I'm back home now,
OL,12,Fit's still difficult on my wife
OL,13,Fbecause I'm not the person she knew in
OL,14,FOctober, and that's a very quick
OL,15,Fchange. It's definitely made things
OL,16,Fworse."
