OL,3,C'Everything is worse': MS stem cell
OL,4,Ctreatment leaves man with side effects
OL,6,FAsked if he regretted having the
OL,7,Ftreatment, he says: "I never regret
OL,8,Fanything in life, I just hope I have
OL,9,Fnot been through all of this, for
OL,10,Fnothing."
OL,12,FThe has said that HSCT () has provided
OL,13,Fmany patients with relapsing MS an
OL,14,Fimprovement in symptoms.
OL,16,FClinical trials showed 99% of people
OL,17,Ftreated had no relapse for one year,
OL,18,Fand 94% of those in the trial didn't
OL,19,Fsee their disability get worse for
OL,20,Fthree years.
